		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Plus if your stack is split on the page boundary, you'll have problems with reading pushed values:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">TSX<br />LDA $103,X&nbsp; ; read 3rd-last pushed value -- will not work if SP wrapped<br /></div>

		

		</td>
