	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On reset and power-up, $00 is internally written to $4017 before the CPU starts execution. This begins the 4-step sequence and enables the APU's frame IRQ flag (but the I flag is set so it won't occur until a CLI or equivalent).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
